  <brief_title>Cisplatin With Gemcitabine With Dexamethasone in Patients With Aggressive Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of Cisplatin With Gemcitabine in Fixed Dose Rate Infusion and Dexamethasone in Second-Line in Patients With Aggressive Non-Hodgkin’s Lymphoma</official_title>
