  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study it to evaluate efficacy of gemcitabine with cisplatin and
      dexamethasone in patients with aggressive non-Hodgkin's lymphoma who have previously
      progressed on first line of chemotherapy with anthracyclines.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
